Title: Facet-based Learning for Statistics  
Author: David Madigan Douglas B Clarkson Deborah Donnell Earl Hunt Michelle Keim Jim Minstrell Martha Nason Andrew Schaffner Chris T. Volinsky 
Keyword: Collaborative learning, cognitive science, instructional computing, statistics education, worldwide web.  
Address: Box 354322  Seattle, WA 98195  
Affiliation: 2 Department of Psychology, University of Washington, 3 Mathsoft, Inc., 4 Mercer Island High School 1 Department of Statistics,  University of Washington  
Email: email: -madigan,keim,andrew,volinsky-@stat.washington.edu, -clarkson, deborah-@statsci.com, ehunt,mnason-@u.washington.edu, jminstrl@nwnet.org  
